cat << "EOF" > /tmp/output
data
EOF

----------------------------------------------------

[
	["function", "cat"],
	["operator", ["<<"]],
	["string", [
		"\"EOF\"",
		["bash", [
			["operator", [">"]],
			" /tmp/output"
		]],
		"\r\ndata\r\nEOF"
	]]
]

----------------------------------------------------

Checks that commands inside quoted here-documents are tokenized as Bash code.
